description: Deletes an OpenSearch Serverless-managed interface endpoint. For more information, see Access Amazon OpenSearch Serverless using an interface endpoint.

parameters.name: clientToken
parameters.description: Unique, case-sensitive identifier to ensure idempotency of the request. This field is autopopulated if not provided.

nested_items.name: id
nested_items.description: The unique identifier of the endpoint.

nested_items.name: status
nested_items.description: The current status of the endpoint deletion process.
